# Version Conventions

## App (Android)
- Format: `vX.Y.Z` (e.g. `v2.2.1`)
- APK filename: `openRS_vX.Y.Z.apk`
- Git tag: `android-vX.Y.Z`

## Firmware (openrs-fw)
- Format: `vX.Y` — no patch digit (e.g. `v1.3`, not `v1.3.0`)
- Binary filename: `openrs-fw-usb_vXYZ.bin` (e.g. `openrs-fw-usb_v130.bin` for v1.3)
- Git tag: `fw-vX.Y`
- `focusrs.h` `OPENRS_FW_VERSION` and `firmware/patches/apply_patches.py` `OPENRS_FW_VERSION` must always match

## Version badge
The version badge lives in the **root `README.md`** only (not `android/README.md`).
